局副局长和分管大气污染防治工作的总工。会上大气处处长陈文涛就天河区的油烟监控取得的成效面向全省推广。', '', '0', '/Uploads/Images/2018-08-01/5b610991727c3.jpg');
INSERT INTO `xg_article` VALUES ('96', '天河区油烟项目成果面向全国推广', '<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;\">2014年5月27、28日两天，广东省环保厅组织了全省的大气污染防治宣贯会，与会人员是各地级市环保局副局长和分管大气污染防治工作的总工。会上大气处处长陈文涛就天河区的油烟监控取得的成效面向全省推广。宣贯会上，省环保厅透露，为解决城市餐饮油烟扰民和监管难等问题，广东计划在珠三角各地级以上市选择典型区域开展规模化餐饮油烟在线监控试点，建立长效机制，管住扰民的油烟。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 28px\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 2em;\"><img src=\"http://m.zhenghonghj.com/Upload/image/201801/20180130095752_2989.jpg\" alt=\"\"/>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 28px\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;\">下午，相关人员去到天河环保局参观广州正虹在天河区油烟监控的第一个试点示范工程，并就油烟监控工作取得的成效进行现场参观交流。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;\">&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p>', '1533086126', '0', '', '', '2014年5月27、28日两天，广东省环保厅组织了全省的大气污染防治宣贯会，与会人员是各地级市环保局副局长和分管大气污染防治工作的总工。会上大气处处长陈文涛就天河区的油烟监控取得的成效面向全省推广。宣贯会上...', '/Uploads/Images/2018-08-01/5b610978a0a6c.jpg', '22', '1533086147', '本站', '0', 'admin', '', '0', '0', '2014年5月27、28日两天，广东省环保厅组织了全省的大气污染防治宣贯会，与会人员是各地级市环保局副局长和分管大气污染防治工作的总工。会上大气处处长陈文涛就天河区的油烟监控取得的成效面向全省推广。', '', '0', '/Uploads/Images/2018-08-01/5b610991727c3.jpg');
INSERT INTO `xg_article` VALUES ('97', '正虹喜迎CCTV《影响力对话》栏目组实地采访', '<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">2014年9月10日，中央电视台《影响力对话》栏目组就中国品牌扶持计划广东省赛区复选来到广州正虹进行实地考察，并展开对公司亚运会空气保障项目餐饮油烟监控事业进行专访，公司全体上下一片欢腾。<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">CCTV《影响力对话》栏目是一档通过访谈优秀企业和杰出人物，展示企业品牌、人物、产品、技术、服务，让发展中企业展示潜力和信心，推动地方优秀企业知名全国的公益性栏目。正虹有幸从三百多家企业中脱颖而进入推荐计划第二阶段，而栏目组此次实地走访正是为了对正虹进一步深入了解。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">栏目组采编中心总监与公司总经理谷育钢进行了密切交谈，他了解到未来3至5年餐饮油烟监控作为正虹的重点品牌打造业务，源于广东省亚运会空气质量保障项目，系统的发展依赖于自主的研发实力，目前，正虹油烟监控系统已经实现从V1.0到V5.0的全新升级换代；市场方面，广州、上海、杭州、无锡等地均已进驻，开展规模试点；目前整个政策支持力度与日俱增，市场前景一片大好。<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>CCTV 《影响力栏目组》实地拍摄</strong><br/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://m.zhenghonghj.com/Upload/image/201801/20180129104902_2373.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" height=\"450\" width=\"600\"/><br/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://m.zhenghonghj.com/Upload/image/201801/20180129105118_4727.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" height=\"450\" width=\"600\"/><br/></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 28px\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">接着，栏目组就公司整体文化氛围进行了“大扫荡”。从前台到会议室，从工作区到到休闲吧，采集十分周全仔细，一行文字，一个记录，一本画册，一个视频，一幅屏风都被摄像机一一捕捉。整个过程中采编小组都充满了极大兴趣，全体正虹人也都十分欣喜和感动。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">此次CCTV《影响力对话》栏目组的到来充分展示了正虹做事的态度，树立品牌的决心和环保服务的理念。全体正虹人都信心满满，展望未来，为改善人们的生存环境提高人们的生活品质而不断努力着。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>参观车间</strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 28px\"><img src=\"http://m.zhenghonghj.com/Upload/image/201801/20180129105208_6680.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 28px\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 28px\"><img src=\"http://m.zhenghonghj.com/Upload/image/201801/20180129105349_1250.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 28px\"><img src=\"http://m.zhenghonghj.com/Upload/image/201801/20180129105208_9327.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>', '1533105125', '1', '', '', '2014年9月10日，中央电视台《影响力对话》栏目组就中国品牌扶持计划广东省赛区复选来到广州正虹进行实地考察，并展开对公司亚运会空气保障项目餐饮油烟监控事业进行专访，公司全体上下一片欢腾。 CCTV《影响力对...', '/Uploads/Images/2018-08-01/5b6153d316df5.jpg', '22', '1534125057', '本站', '0', 'admin', '{\\\"0\\\":\\\"\\\\/Uploads\\\\/Images\\\\/2018-08-01\\\\/5b6153db39141.jpg\\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"\\\\/Uploads\\\\/Images\\\\/2018-08-01\\\\/5b6153dabcc4d.jpg\\\"}', '9', '1534433515', '2014年9月10日，中央电视台《影响力对话》栏目组就中国品牌扶持计划广东省赛区复选来到广州正虹进行实地考察，并展开对公司亚运会空气保障项目餐饮油烟监控事业进行专访。', '', '0', '/Uploads/Images/2018-08-01/5b6153d68592e.jpg');
INSERT INTO `xg_article` VALUES ('98', '广州市东濠涌水质在线监测', '<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 28px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>国内城市河道治理监管标杆—广州市东濠涌水质在线监测系统</strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><strong><br/></strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>一、项目背景</strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">东濠涌是广州现存唯一一条贯穿市中心的河涌，2010年在越秀区政府的努力下完成水质的净化处理，实现东濠涌绿色生态的全面恢复。同时，东濠涌通过与新河浦涌、东山湖的调水补水工程，共同构成一个水体循环系统，扩大和巩固东濠涌治水成果，助力修复新河浦涌、东山湖生态环境。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">东濠涌、新河浦涌和东山湖的综合整治和调水补水不可一蹴而就，大量的水质监测数据能够为水体循环系统提供有效的环境事件决策支持。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">东濠涌水质监测项目是目前国内城市河道监管的首个成功案例，具有重大的政治意义，上一届人大常委中有五位先后来过现场考察。今年年初，习近平主席也曾到东濠涌现场进行考察。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>习主席到东濠涌现场考察</strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: center\"><img width=\"524\" height=\"299\" src=\"/Upload/image/20180809/1533786281513627.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>二、总体目标</strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">通过“东濠涌水质在线监测系统”建设，实现对东濠涌下游水域水质指标的自动监测和水质评价，提高环境监测部门的工作效率和监管能力，为东濠涌、新河浦涌和东山湖综合整治和调水补水提供数据支撑和决策支持；为水体突发环境事件提供预警，以便环保和相关职能部门能及时进行应急处置。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">通过越秀区环保局水质监控中心数据管理和决策支持系统的建设，实现仪器设备的远程管理，水质监测数据的显示、编辑、打印、查询、统计、分析、告警、存储和传输等，并通过数学模型的建立为环境管理提供决策支持服务。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>三、总体思路</strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">本项目我公司承担建设的“东濠涌水质在线监测系统”，是在东濠涌下游东山湖指定区域建设现场端水质自动监测站，通过3G无线通讯技术，将现场端采集到的水质指标（高锰酸盐指数、氨氮、总磷、总氮、pH值、电导率、水温、浊度、溶解氧，可扩展）数据远程传输到广州市越秀区环境保护局内水质监控中心数据管理和决策支持系统，实现地图监测、表格监测、告警查询、查询统计、综合分析、决策支持等功能。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">系统整体结构图如下所示：</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: center\"><img width=\"554\" height=\"397\" src=\"/Upload/image/20180809/1533786282373687.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>四、硬件设备选择</strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">水站建设模式综合考虑本区域站点现场实际情况，通过各种模式的比较，选择最优模式，监测设备是拥有国内外先进技术的设备——整体自动监测水站。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: center\"><img width=\"554\" height=\"367\" src=\"/Upload/image/20180809/1533786283372267.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">整体式水站在本区域项目的应用中有着明显的优势。整体柜式水质自动监测站是以现场水质监测为目的来开发的多参数、智能化的水质分析仪。可同时实现多个水质指标的实时测量、显示、存储和传输。仪器本身集成了数据采集装置、工业控制计算机和通讯传输设备，能够实现水质的长期在线监测和数据的无/有线远程传输，是环境监测、总量控制、事故预警和地表/地下水资源监测的最佳选择。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>现场实拍图</strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: center\"><img width=\"499\" height=\"639\" src=\"/Upload/image/20180809/1533786285124413.jpg\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>五、系统功能介绍</strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">1、实时监控模块</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">地图监控模块实现展示越秀区水体流域基本信息，帮助环保局监管人员了解流域附近的地理信息，实现在线监测数据的实时刷新、超标告警，为水体突发环境事件提供预警，以便环保和相关职能部门能及时进行应急处置。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>在线监控软件界面截图</strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: center\"><img width=\"554\" height=\"208\" src=\"/Upload/image/20180809/1533786287668154.jpg\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: center\"><img width=\"554\" height=\"257\" src=\"/Upload/image/20180809/1533786288629124.jpg\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">列表监测模块是将水质的监测数据通过表格的形式完整的显示出来，包括监测点时间、各监测指标名称、指标数据等，同时以图表的形式生动形象的显示出各类数据，以EXCEL报表形式打印或另存。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">2、超标告警模块</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">超标告警的告警内容包括告警时间、监测因子、告警值、水质标准、告警描述（超标、异常），需告警的监测因子、告警值、水质标准可根据用户要求自行设置，告警资料可导出到EXCEL文档中，或者打印出来，仪器校准、标定以及超出仪器检出限的数据需单独做好标识，此类数据不参与告警计算。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">3、查询统计模块</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">运营记录以独立界面查询显示自动监测站的运营记录及仪器的校准信息，支持导出Excel与打印功能。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">统计报表用户自由选择水质评价标准、评价方法。根据所选标准、方法对水体进行评价，按设定的时间段查询正常监控数据并进行统计，制作出包含平均值、最大值、最小值、最值出现时间点、超标值、超标倍数等内容的表格、以及水质变化过程曲线图、柱状图，设定的时间段内各类水质占比的饼图。系统自动生成日、月、年报，以表格和统计图表的形式进行历史数据比较。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">4、水质人工监测数据管理</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">为更好地实现水质评价和决策支持等功能，系统除建立水质在线监测系统数据库外，还需建立和管理水质人工监测数据。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">5、决策支持模块</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">通过系统内置的环境资料及数学模型，使管理者在查询指标时了解基本的处置方法、应急监测方法、环境标准，法律法规等辅助信息，同时对“调水补水”、“水体富营养化计算”、“蓝藻水华预警”和“水质平均污染指数计算”等提供决策支持。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">6、后台管理模块</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">东濠涌基本信息管理、指标配置、应急方案管理、法律法规管理、用户信息管理、用户权限管理。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p>', '1533786339', '1', '', '', '国内城市河道治理监管标杆—广州市东濠涌水质在线监测系统一、项目背景 东濠涌是广州现存唯一一条贯穿市中心的河涌，2010年在越秀区政府的努力下完成水质的净化处理，实现东濠涌绿色生态的全面恢复。同时，东濠涌...', '/Uploads/Images/2018-08-09/5b6bb8e0cd364.jpg', '32', '1534214932', '本站', '0', 'admin', '{\\\"0\\\":\\\"\\\\/Uploads\\\\/Images\\\\/2018-08-14\\\\/5b7242c9bcee6.jpg\\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"\\\\/Uploads\\\\/Images\\\\/2018-08-14\\\\/5b7242c03fd3f.jpg\\\"}', '22', '1538657864', '东濠涌是广州现存唯一一条贯穿市中心的河涌，2010年在越秀区政府的努力下完成水质的净化处理，实现东濠涌绿色生态的全面恢复。同时，东濠涌通过与新河浦涌、东山湖的调水补水工程，共同构成一个水体循环系统，扩大和巩固东濠涌治水成果，助力修复新河浦涌、东山湖生态环境。', '', '0', '');
INSERT INTO `xg_article` VALUES ('99', '2018年', '', '1528358581', '1', '', '', '', '/Uploads/Images/2018-08-09/5b6c0d6156464.jpg', '53', '1533808004', '本站', '0', 'admin', '', '0', '0', '至今已累计获得45项国家软件著作权、12项广东省高新技术产品、5项发明专利；<br/>\n更名为广州正虹环境科技有限公司；<br/>\n参加第十六届中国国家环保展览会；<br/>\n新一代油烟在线监控仪发布；<br/>\n河北任县、邢台等地油烟在线监控系统建设；<br/>\n中集集团废气处理工程建设；', '', '0', '');
INSERT INTO `xg_article` VALUES ('100', '2017年', '', '1502266358', '1', '', '', '', '/Uploads/Images/2018-08-09/5b6c0dcb356f2.jpg', '52', '1533809911', '本站', '0', 'admin', '', '0', '0', '累计获得39项国家软件著作权、7项广东省高新技术产品、5项发明专利<br/>\n正虹环境在线监控系统涵盖油烟、VOCs、烟气、ＰＭ2.5、扬尘、水质等在线监控；<br/>\n连续5年获得守合同重信用企业证书；<br/>\n河北廊坊、陕西咸阳、晋城等正虹油烟在线监测系统建成投入运营；<br/>\n承建了上海太太乐、南雄污水处理厂、信华精机等知名企业VOCs处理工程；<br/>\n参加第三届中国环博会（广州展）；', '', '0', '');
INSERT INTO `xg_article` VALUES ('101', '2016年', '', '1462954498', '1', '', '', '', '/Uploads/Images/2018-08-09/5b6c0e1a576cc.jpg', '51', '1533809941', '本站', '0', 'admin', '', '0', '0', '通过ISO14001环境管理体系认证、OHSMS18001职业健康安全管理体系认证通过知识产权管理体系认证；<br/>\n东莞、中山、佛山等地正虹油烟在线监测系统建成投入运营；<br/>\n正虹环境承建清远污水在线监控系统建成投入运营；<br/>\n公司研发的VOCs治理技术、产品在全国推广应用；', '', '0', '');
