INSERT INTO `xg_category` VALUES ('12', '4G视频环保数采仪', 'Company Profiles', '3', '/Uploads/Images/2018-06-06/5b17846b1284b.png', 'Product/lists', '0', '2', '0', '0', '0', '<p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 127, 229)\">产品概述</span></strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">正虹环保4G视频数据采集仪，简称4G视频数采仪，是按照《污染源在线自动监控（监测）数据采集传输仪技术要求》（HJ 477）的标准开发的新一代智能数据采集器，是GPRS数据采集仪的升级版，在传统数据采集仪的基础上具备接入4G无线网络功能，并能实现视频数据采集，使原来需要两张数据通新卡变为只采用一张卡，同时也精简了4G路由器，并包含了多种常见的通信方式，技术要求和性能指标达到并优于标准中的要求。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 28px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Upload/image/20180606/1528267478137873.jpg\"/><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">软件上，完全支持《污染源在线自动监控（监测）系统数据传输标准》（HJ/T 212）通信协议。采集器配备的以太网接口，既可以使用现场已有的局域网宽带网络通信，也可以自行直接通过ADSL拨号上网。采集器配备的GPRS通信功能，使设备在没有有线网络可用的情况下，能通过GPRS/4G无线通信方式，与监控中心保持正常的通信。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">正虹环保4G视频数据采集仪，是新一代环境监测、污染源监控专用数据采集器，按照工业级标准设计，针对环境监测的各种要求做了专门的优化，坚固耐用，满足恶劣的监控环境要求，配备了丰富齐全的通信接口，支持局域网、ADSL、GPRS、&nbsp;4G等，满足不同现场环境下对远程通信的要求。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 127, 229)\">系统原理</span></strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">监控系统是物联网在环保领域的应用，即物联网的三层结构，前端感知层、传输层、后端软件，通过此技术原理，实现监控24小时不间断的监控。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 127, 229)\">产品特色</span></strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">新一代智能数据采集器，在传统数据采集仪的基础上具备接入4G无线网络功能。能实现视频数据采集，使原来需要两张数据卡变为只采用一张，精简了4G路由器。配备7英寸高清触摸屏，随时查看实时数据和历史数据。内置蓄电池，断电可工作72小时。丰富的采集控制端口①。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">◆<strong>环保认证</strong>：</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">通过中国环保设备认证（CEP认证）</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">内置国内主流仪器厂商通讯协议。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">全面符合数据采集器行业标准②。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">◆<strong>调试方便</strong>：</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">根据用户设置自动对各种前端仪表进行采集和控制，无需修改程序。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">正确设置即可正常使用，无需进行二次开发，支持远程升级。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">支持第三方的上位机通信协议，可导出历史数据，</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">支持多中心通信，可同时与多个后台服务器按不同协议进行通信。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">◆<strong>坚固耐用</strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">超2万小时不间断运行</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">采用工业级设计标准，达到IP65防护等级</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">可靠的软件系统</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">通过恶劣环境使用考验</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 127, 229)\">系统构成</span></strong></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><strong>水质</strong>：一个典型的污水排放口，常需要采集监控如下参数：流量值，PH值，COD，氨氮，各种重金属含量，如镍、铅、汞、铜等。因此污水监测需要配置流量计、PH计、COD在线监测仪、氨氮在线监测仪和各种重金属在线监测仪等分析仪器，以及数据采集器，数据采集器必须具有多种数据采集手段，能有效管理这些分析仪器，汇总从分析仪器得到的数据，并将数据自动上报到环保部门的污染源在线监控平台。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><strong>废气</strong>：对废气的监控一般采集：烟气流速、浓度以及硫化氢、二氧化碳、氨、二氧化硫等污染物的含量。常用的方法是安装一套CEMS烟气连续在线监控系统和一台数据采集器。由烟气在线监控系统分析各污染物数据，由数据采集器负责采集和上报各污染物数据。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><strong>传输</strong>：由于污染源的地理位置分布范围广，而且分散，现场的数据只能用远程通信的方式来实现自动上报。常用的通信方式有公网和专网，有线网络和无线网络之分。</p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '', '', '产品概述正虹环保4G视频数据采集仪，简称4G视频数采仪，是按照《污染源在线自动监控（监测）数据采集传输仪技术要求》（HJ 477）的标准开发的新一代智能数据采集器，是GPRS数据采集仪的升级版，在传统数据采集仪...', '正虹环保4G视频数据采集仪是按照《污染源在线自动监控（监测）数据采集传输仪技术要求》（HJ 477）的标准开发的新一代智能数据采集器，是GPRS数据采集仪的升级版', '');
