n style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"/Upload/image/20180606/1528268901114206.jpg\"/><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;margin-left: 0;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 28px;text-align: justify\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong><strong>测量范围：</strong><strong>0~200mg/m</strong><strong>³</strong></strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong><strong>误差</strong><strong>≤</strong><strong>10%</strong></strong></span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word;font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica;font-size: 12px;line-height: 18px;white-space: normal\"><br/></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>多数据采集，参数补偿</strong>：通过专利技术采集油烟数据以及温度、湿度和气压等多种参数，并通过数学模型计算出较高准确度的油烟浓度。</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>自动清洁传感器功能</strong>：探头能有效抵抗油烟污染，具有自动清洁传感器的功能，使用维护简单，维护成本低，维护周期一年以上；</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong>拆除报警</strong>：具备断线、断电及探头失效等自动检测报警功能，防止人为破坏</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><