体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; widows: auto; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">■量程开关可选择多个不同的量程，适应多种VOC气体的检测</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; widows: auto; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &#39;sans serif&#39;, tahoma, verdana, helvetica; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; widows: auto; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">■系统可监测多种有机废气，可根据不同客户的监测需求定制具有优越的扩展性</span></p><p><br/></p>', '1528269637', '1', '', '', '', '/Uploads/Images/2018-06-06/5b178b2e99f46.png', '16', '1528269637', '0', '', null, '36', '', '', '', '', '0', '9999', '0', '', '', '', '', 'ZH-VOCs5100T挥发性有机物VOCs在线监测系统是一款基于气相色谱技术的在线监测系统，该系统采用光离子化检测器PID，可对30多种挥发性有机物（VOCs），如苯，甲苯，二甲苯有灵敏响应，精准检测。', '0', '0', '');
